{"word":"H4222 - מָחָא - mâchâʼ - maw-khaw' - Clap","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מָחָא</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>mâchâʼ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>maw-khaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Clap"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கொட்டு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to strike, to clap (the hands)"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to clap (of joy)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel) to clap (of exultation)"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>rub</i> or <i>strike</i> the hands together (in exultation): - clap."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}